What is Gary Dubin's famous for?

Gary Michael Dubin was an American actor. He was best known for his portrayal of Punky Lazaar, a friend of Danny's on The Partridge Family. He also voiced Toulouse in The Aristocats in 1970 and played the part of ill-fated teenager Eddie Marchand, who was eaten by the shark in Jaws 2.. You can find more here.
